highlights.text: “The Glen - Levi Heron Edit” by Levi Heron has been on Viral Songs United Kingdom the longest, at 90 days straight.
KPop Demon Hunters Cast has the most spots on Viral Songs United Kingdom. “Golden” is the highest at #2.
